---
title: Thai-Style Fried Rice with Makrut Lime & Chilli Fried Egg
description: Add the classic Thai flavours of sweet chilli sauce, shredded coconut and makrut lime to fried rice to create a comforting dish that tastes totally new. Top it with a chilli fried egg, roasted peanuts and crispy shallots for a touch of decadence.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/thai-style-fried-rice-836d6ec3.jpg
